Gesper shook the hand back. Feeling he would be better received in bot 
mode, he transformed, pronouncing the traditionnal "I am tansformed" 
line.

Gesper: Good to meet you too, Hoist. Can one of you tell me how many 
warriors there are in your group?

> Hoist held out his hand, and shook firmly. "Good to meet you Gesper,

back
> at the ship, then to Gesper again. "How observant of you. Our ship 
is
> not a war ship, really it is a classified stealth shuttle."

> Pacifix looked to the shuttle. "Crossroads, Klant, Torca, Artemis,
